li>\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.4em;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:24px 8px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"leaf\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第三种是正常 Graph 模式，它的优点是首请求没有延迟，也不需要预先占用资源，适合中等规模、启动频率不高的常规部署场景。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"leaf\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户可以根据自己的业务需求灵活选择最合适的模式。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"leaf\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.4009259259259259\" width=\"677px\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 660.969px !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f5893c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOqSXUEEBrdvEQmzEQp7IQxuqgqQAsiaKtrMicv96wibXj5sl6GmsIQBsqBKYU9CuRkiaCO3cXwD5jeCg5wicOnDOSic5ukjHmuulwdNDsKrbEY4Fc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D7\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"leaf\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot